==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Genouillre
<hw>Ge*nouil`l⟦egrave⟧re"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[F.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Anc. Armor)</fld> <def>A metal plate
covering the knee.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Fort.)</fld> <def>That part of a parapet which lies
between the gun platform and the bottom of an embrasure.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>-genous</ent>⟦br⟧
